snippet.title: UM: 'Face Your Fears' Update (Featuring Wixie, The Delinquent!)
snippet.description:
Wixie The Delinquent arrives in the constant to cause trouble. 

Walter the Fearless, and his trusty companion Woby are here to put everything back together!

Download Uncompromising Mode: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfile...

A Puzzle To Be Solved: https://discord.com/invite/KMAVp9Kt6d

Check out our Official Discord: https://discord.gg/DFnDuCyp8H

Browse our wiki for more info: https://uncompromisingmode.wiki.gg/
